The paper proposes a deep learning model for traffic flow prediction, which involves the use of neural networks and time series analysis. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also involves the use of image processing techniques, which could place it in the sub-category cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper deals with traffic flow analysis, which could place it in the sub-category cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
